item.dc:creator: @Vince Vince`
item.description:
@Vince wrote:

Do you have a Format Disc or File in your computer? If so, Format your computer. But note that everything from the Drive will be erased. Then Re-Install it. It should then work since it will clear the SYSTEM32 Folder Under Your C: Drive.

Else, I can’t help
